movies.title: Made in Dagenham
movies.plot: A dramatization of the 1968 strike at the Ford Dagenham car plant, where female workers walked out in protest against sexual discrimination.
movies.awards: Nominated for 3 BAFTA Film Awards. Another 3 wins & 14 nominations.

events.title: the Ford sewing machinists go on strike

movies.title: Stoned
movies.plot: A chronicle of the sordid life and suspicious death of Rolling Stones co-founder Brian Jones, who was found in the bottom of his swimming pool weeks after being let go from the band.
